OL,3,CLast remaining Channel Island Normandy
OL,4,CVeteran shares his memories
OL,6,FThe last Normandy Veteran from the ,
OL,7,FErnest Thorne laid a wreath in Jersey
OL,8,Ftoday to mark the .
OL,10,FErnest Thorne from Jersey arrived on
OL,11,FJuno Beach alongside 150,000 allied
OL,12,Ftroops in June 1944, he says: "We were
OL,13,Fresponsible for repairing any
OL,14,Fvehicles, that broke down and any
OL,15,Fmachinery that broke down and when we
OL,16,Flanded we went to Caen and that was in
OL,17,Fa mess.
