OL,3,CLast remaining Channel Island Normandy
OL,4,CVeteran shares his memories
OL,6,FBut he thinks the men he served with
OL,7,Fare, he explains: "Oh yes, every one
OL,8,Fof them, lovely friends."
OL,10,F"When you are in the front line and
OL,11,Fyou are getting fired at, land mines
OL,12,Fand everything is going off, some
OL,13,Fpeople can't take it, their mind goes,
OL,14,Fthey are people who become ill."
