OL,3,CLast remaining Channel Island Normandy
OL,4,CVeteran shares his memories
OL,6,FHe also remembers those veterans who
OL,7,Fnever came home, he explains: "There
OL,8,Fwas an awful lot who never got off the
OL,9,Fbeaches alive, when I landed on the
OL,10,Fbeaches it was crowded but then it was
OL,11,Fkind of organised chaos and it was a
OL,12,Fbit noisy.
OL,14,F"But yes, there was an awful lot who
OL,15,Fnever got off the beach, it was
OL,16,Fterrible"
OL,18,FHe adds: "They should always be
OL,19,Fremembered, and D-Day, we should never
OL,20,Fforget it."
