OL,3,CLast remaining Channel Island Normandy
OL,4,CVeteran shares his memories
OL,6,F"I often think of the people that I
OL,7,Fknew and I wonder what they are doing
OL,8,Fnow. I hope people remember the good
OL,9,Fthings I did."
OL,11,F"I survived and when I look back, I
OL,12,Fdon't have a total recall. The things
OL,13,FI do remember, some good, some bad but
OL,14,FI had some lovely friends."
