OL,3,CLast remaining Channel Island Normandy
OL,4,CVeteran shares his memories
OL,6,F, Queen Camilla, Prince William and
OL,7,Fthe UK Prime Minister Rishi Sunak at a
OL,8,FD-Day in Portsmouth ahead of the 80th
OL,9,Fanniversary on Wednesday 5 June, he
OL,10,Freflects: "The ceremony was tear-
OL,11,Fjerking that was, I have never known
OL,12,Fanything like it in my life."
OL,14,F"There was someone in front of me who
OL,15,Fhad his legs blown off and a lot of
OL,16,Fchildren talking about their great-
OL,17,Fgrandfathers, and you think well that
OL,18,Fcould have happened to me but I am
OL,19,Fvery lucky because I survived all of
OL,20,Fthat."
