OL,3,CLast remaining Channel Island Normandy
OL,4,CVeteran shares his memories
OL,6,FErnest adds: "I am really lucky
OL,7,Fbecause I survived all of that, but in
OL,8,Fthe army, you have friends around you
OL,9,Fwho have the same mind as you, so if
OL,10,Fyou are in trouble you are surrounded
OL,11,Fby your friends and that was a great
OL,12,Fhelp.
OL,14,FHe says he shared jokes with His
OL,15,FMajesty the King at the special event,
OL,16,Fhe recalls: "We had a good laugh, it
OL,17,Fwas really good. All the people that
OL,18,Fwere involved were wonderful."
