OL,4,CVeteran shares his memories
OL,6,FThe Normandy Veteran says he hopes to
OL,7,Fbe remembered in a good way, he says:
OL,8,F"I hope that my family would say well
OL,9,Fdad was a good fella."
OL,11,F"I've got a wonderful family, I have
OL,12,Fgot a wonderful wife but I don't know
OL,13,Fhow I will be remembered."
OL,15,FA portrait of Ernest Thorne was
OL,16,Funveiled at a special ceremony in St
OL,17,FHelier on Friday 31 May.
